  "instructions": [
    "Brush both sides of the tortilla wraps with vegetable oil.",
    "Place the wraps in a large steamer basket, leaving a small space between each wrap.",
    "Steam the wraps for 5 minutes, or until slightly softened and pliable.",
    "In a small pan, heat the cumin, coriander, garlic, ginger, salt, and black pepper over medium heat, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the crushed peanut brittle to the pan and stir for 1 minute, or until fragrant.",
    "Spread a tablespoon of cream cheese onto the center of each wrap.",
    "Add a spoonful of the peanut brittle mixture on top of the cream cheese.",
    "Drizzle with honey, lemon juice, and sesame seeds.",
    "Garnish with chopped parsley, cilantro, and a sprinkle of sesame seeds.",
    "Serve warm, with additional harissa on the side for added heat.",
    "Slice into wedges for a delicious brunch dish."
  ],
